      "comment": "ADD A ZERO (6) racing well without winning, placing at her last five runs. Last start finished 2nd over 380m at this track beaten 3.5 lengths (21.87) behind Mizuki Heart in a Grade 5 on July 17. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Makes plenty of appeal. HIGH GEAR MARIA (8) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 6 lengths into third (22.58) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 380m. Leading player again. PANAMA LOCO (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording three placings in a row before finishing seventh (23.30) at this track latest. Deserves plenty of respect.",
